R. E. ARBUTHNOT et al. v. Bonnie DEVERICK. No. 5448. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Aug. 1, 1956. Royce, Hampton, Dunham, Royce & Engleman, Salina, Kan., for appellants. Morris, Bailey & Kiser, Wichita, Kan., for appellee.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge.

Docketed and dismissed on motion of appellee, for failure of appellants diligently to prosecute.
